中國政府注意到這個運動，外交部發言人華春瑩在2月12日[告訴](https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2019/02/12/world/asia/ap-
as-china-turkey.html)記者：

> China has more than 1 billion people, do we need to release a video of
> everyone?

> 中國有超過十億的人口，難道我們要公布每一個人的影片？

母親還在新疆再教育營的推特用戶@ferkat_jawdat選擇用一種嘲諷的方式重述中國政府上述的發言，指出中國對新疆人進行[大規模的監視行動](https://www.businessinsider.com/xianjiang-
province-china-police-state-surveillance-2018-7)：

> At a regular news briefing on Tuesday, Chinese foreign ministry spokeswoman
> Hua Chunying said of the
> [#MeTooUyghur](https://twitter.com/hashtag/MeTooUyghur?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)
> campaign, “China has more than 1 billion people, do we need to release a
> video of everyone?” YES, you can, since u have 2 camera for every person!!!
